# mysql_replication_hostgroups removed - not compatible with master-master setup
# For master-master, ProxySQL uses weight-based routing within hostgroup 0
# Both masters are always in hostgroup 0, ProxySQL routes to highest weight ONLINE server

# Scheduler removed - not needed for master-master setup
# ProxySQL will use weight-based routing and monitoring for failover

